fulltitle: Jazz Legends Dave Brubeck, Ramses Lewis and Dr. Billy Taylor
description: Legendary composers and jazz pianists Ramses Lewis ("The In Crowd"), Dave Brubeck ("Take Five"), and Dr. Billy Taylor ("I Wish I Knew How It Would Feel To Be Free") discuss the legacy of jazz in this 2008 conversation at the John F. Kennedy Center for the Performing Arts in Washington, DC.
